{"tid":2086640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府宣布港區國安法今日稍後生效","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T11:47:28.000Z","uid":65024,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd0af3780d9c64f65b3effbd662b893538e9aaf","tid":2086640,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db835ed43379d8d46bc5c1ffe9748368491f11c","tid":2086640,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=9956e211\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9665f52fe9b6f01d6b99460fcb00af0bd48ad7f9","tid":2086640,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"7月1日唔撚係慶回歸，係加拿大國慶呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086269</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"133254242df5955474817d60579477b10059279b","tid":2086640,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"條文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aad635112b69c58c39bae9ab8fde38b690ca52","tid":2086640,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"黎la 71照生 ar dllm"},{"pid":"dc80f020a37673c798c5fe53cd132243fbab99f6","tid":2086640,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"條文都未有生咩效？"},{"pid":"b8a21c068b1f16ac89571d877f99cccf5c7beeb4","tid":2086640,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc80f020a37673c798c5fe53cd132243fbab99f6","tid":2086640,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"條文都未有生咩效？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"就係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa233a8fac9e161f